Sentencas: A solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) in which (Ba0.3Sr0.2La0.5)InO2.75 was used as an electrolyte was fabricated in order to characterize its electrical power generation.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using (Ba0.3Sr0.2La0.5)InO2.75 electrolyte

Sentencas: Moistened 1% hydrogen gas balanced with argon gas was used as the fuel gas to prevent reduction of the electrolyte.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using (Ba0.3Sr0.2La0.5)InO2.75 electrolyte

Sentencas: The chemical reaction between the electrolyte and some electrode materials has been investigated by X-ray diffraction.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using (Ba0.3Sr0.2La0.5)InO2.75 electrolyte

Sentencas: The appropriate electrodes are Pt and Ni for the cathode and anode, respectively.
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using (Ba0.3Sr0.2La0.5)InO2.75 electrolyte

Sentencas: The maximum power density was 0.51 (W/cm(2)) at 800 degreesC. (C) 2004
Titulo: Solid oxide fuel cell using (Ba0.3Sr0.2La0.5)InO2.75 electrolyte
